Package asypad.shapes

This package contains the shapes that are used to store the shapes drawn onto the screen by the user.

See: Description

    Circle
    Custom Circle used for drawing in AsyPad.

    Shape
    Custom Shape class that is a superclass for all shapes drawn on AsyPad.
    Utility

Package asypad.shapes Description

This package contains the shapes that are used to store the shapes drawn onto the screen by the user. The superclass, Shape, has 3 subclasses: Point, Line, and Circle. The Utility class provides all the math tools needed to calculate the locations of these shapes.
Author:
Raymond Feng
